package.name: drug-names
package.author: Nick Weatherton
package.description: A quick autocompleteion which contains all US brand and generic drug names as of July 2022. Sourced from RxTerms202207
package.title: US Drug Names

manifest.name: drug-names
manifest.title: US Drug Names
manifest.description: A quick autocompleteion which contains all US brand and generic drug names as of July 2022. Sourced from RxTerms202207
manifest.author: Nick Weatherton

value.readme:
**US Drug Name Autocomplete**

1. Type *ddd*
2. Start typing a brand or generic name of a US drug
3. Never misspell ~~amitryptyline~~ ~~amytriptiline~~ amitriptyline again!
